	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well...
<br />ASL and LSR could work with $00, to write $00, but anyother value will output bus conflicts.
<br />INC and DEC can ONLY lead to bus conflicts.
<br />ROL and ROR would, well, work with $00 and carry clear OR with $ff and carry set, but that's rather crazy.
<br />So yeah, a game could avoid having lda #$00; sta BusConflictZero, but instad have asl BusConflictsZero to switch bank zero, while crazy, it would in theory works.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
